title: WooSwatches 2.5.2 - Woocommerce Color or Image Variation
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Convert your normal variable attribute dropdown select to nicely looking color or image select. You can display images or color in all common size. Display them in round or square mode. WooSwatche WordPress Plugin Features Supports color/image/text variation swatches and dropdown select. Woocommerce improved variable product attributes and attribute swatches. Global color or image values for attributes. Inbuilt color/image product filter. Works on mobile devices. Different sizes of swatch from small to large. Square as well as round swatch support. Option to display option name below swatch. Show selected option name on single product page. Shows color or image swatches on shop/category/tag archive pages
